This is a forked version of

    https://github.com/jimblackler/jsonschemafriend

The fork was created to enable short-term publishing to Maven Central.

The fork is available at

    https://github.com/org-metaeffekt/jsonschemafriend

The following changes were applied:

- the README.md file was extended to describe the purpose of the changes.
- this NOTICE file was added to adopt and adhere to 4.d of the Apache License 2.0.
- pom.xml and libraries/pom.xml were added to faciliate a maven build and apply the standard publishing scheme we use.
- META-INF folders with LICENSE and NOTICE where added.

The original code is under Apache License 2.0.

All changes and add-ons are also license under the Apache License 2.0.

